
# Users & Roles

## 1. User Types
| Role | Permissions | Notes |
|------|------------|------|
| Admin | Full access to system settings, content, and users |  |
| User  | Can register, purchase categories, upgrade, and view own data |  |
| Guest | Can browse basic info only, no purchase or upgrade |  |

## 2. Role Rules
- Each user must be assigned exactly one role.  
- Permissions are enforced automatically by the system.  
- Future roles or exceptions must be documented here.

## 3. Notes
- Keep all role changes and assignments updated in this file.
